    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows signs of regular use over the years. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dents, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear and some staining. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it will likely need some preventative maintenance and minor repairs soon to keep it in reliable shape. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a more accessible price point who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
